//Write a program to find greatest of 2 numbers using functions without arguments..

int main()
{
    void gr();
    gr();
}
void gr()
{
    int a,b;
    printf("\n enter 2 numbers:");
    scanf("%d%d",&a,&b);
    if(a>b)
        printf("\n first number is greater");
    else if(b>a)
        printf("\n second number is greater");
    else
        printf("\n both are same");
}

Output:
enter 2 numbers:
87
54

 first number is greater.

Reference:https://funcodepro.blogspot.com/2018/12/how-to-find-greatest-of-2-numbers-using.html
